data.description: Beautiful Single Story Home on a Corner Lot! 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2,139 square feet, 2 car garage w/ low maintenance yard! Features include new stainless steel appliances, wood, tile, laminate and linoleum flooring throughout home, newer AC installed in 2019, reverse osmosis system in the kitchen sink and so much more! Close to Schools, Shopping, and HWY 99 for those commuters!
